channel.title: Multiplayer Skin Models Have No Eyes
channel.description: Just bought the steam early access version of Black Mesa and I noticed that the multiplayer skins that have customize able faces have no eyes, don't know if that happens in game, but it seemed odd. This supposed to be like that or is this a glitch in the customizer?
